## API Routes

| Method | Route | Auth | Description |
|--------|-------|------|-------------|
| POST | `/api/auth/register` | None | Register student |
| POST | `/api/auth/login` | None | Login → returns JWT |
| GET | `/api/student/houses/:studentId` | JWT | Get assigned houses |
| POST | `/api/visit/verify` | JWT | GPS distance check (< 30m) |
| POST | `/api/patient/record` | JWT | Submit patient data → ML → DB |
| POST | `/api/admin/upload-students` | JWT + Admin | Bulk upload students |
| POST | `/api/admin/upload-houses` | JWT + Admin | Bulk upload houses |
| POST | `/api/admin/run-clustering` | JWT + Admin | ML clustering → store assignments |

