## Security Implemented

- **bcrypt** password hashing (pre-save hook on User model)
- **JWT** on all protected routes via [middleware/auth.js](file:///c:/Users/jdbha/Downloads/village-health-system/backend/middleware/auth.js)
- **helmet** for HTTP security headers
- **CORS** restricted to `ALLOWED_ORIGINS` env variable
- **express-rate-limit** (10 requests / 15min) on auth endpoints
- **express-mongo-sanitize** to prevent NoSQL injection
- **bodyParser limit** set to 10KB
- **Multer** validates file type (jpeg/png/webp) and size (max 5MB)
- Passwords never returned in any API response (`select: false`)
- All secrets stored in `.env` (never hardcoded)

